div.p:
COBIT process becomes OSCAL control with @class='process'. COBIT
        practice (a component of a process) becomes OSCAL enhancement with
        @class='practice'.

stmt.p:
Each IT goal presents an implicit link to an IT goal specified elsewhere in COBITS (the
            Goals Cascade). Here, references to IT goals are indicated by a two-digit numeric
          identifier (01-17) and a title, and glossed with a brief statement, Metrics. These
          are captured inside the enhancement as prop with
          @class='number', title and stmt with
          @class='metrics'.
